		<page mustlisten="false" obfuscate="false" length="16511">
			<text><![CDATA[This picture shows the circulation of air across the world. Easterly winds blow from the East. Westerly winds blow from the West. Northerly winds blow from the North. Southerly winds blow from the South. In the northern hemisphere polar air comes from the North.]]></text>
