		<page mustlisten="false" obfuscate="false" length="15596">
			<text><![CDATA[There are many variable winds in the northern and southern hemispheres. There are also local winds in different parts of the world such as the Mistral in the south of France or the Bora in the Adriatic Sea. They are seasonal winds and regional winds.]]></text>
